Loeffingen: Köpfler still the only candidate
Information on the Internet: Although the Baar town Loeffingen can be described as attractive city with its 7514 inhabitants, an intact infrastructure, a forward-looking school, children, youth and older persons, as well as its own municipal utility, has so far been reported yet no other candidate for mayor.
As the only candidate for the succession of not more candidates on grounds of age Mayor Norbert Brugger has so far been the 46-year-old banker and economist Dieter Köpfler from Loeffingen.
The application deadline is Monday, 11 November, from 18 clock.
